About Us
Locally owned and operated in Keystone Heights, FL, Johnny’s BBQ has been an icon in the community since they first opened their doors in 1988. What started out as a quaint, 15-table restaurant has since grown to be the most iconic & loved restaurant in town - serving over a million pounds of BBQ since they’ve been in business.
Johnny's has served as a Partner in Education with Clay County Schools, been a Super Chief Sponsor for Keystone Heights High School football team, a Charter Member of the Lake Regions Kiwanis Club & has been an active member in many of the lake area ministries.
Because of their loyal guests they have been blessed to consistently give back to the community and are grateful for the continued opportunity to serve.
